del-and-state-machine.yolopilot.md:635:    ./prompts/40-genre-selection-api-and-ui.md:17:- Genre selection stage UI\\nprompts/10-domain-model-and-state-machine.yolopilot.md:636:    ./prompts/40-genre-selection-api-and-ui.md:23:- The selected genre survives page refresh and session resume.\\nprompts/10-domain-model-and-state-machine.yolopilot.md:655:    ./prompts/10-domain-model-and-state-machine.md:10:- Define the major entities: story session, workflow stage, genre, tone profile, story brief, pitch, selected pitch, character sheet, beat sheet, story setup, composition segment, audio job, export asset, and event log entry.\\nprompts/10-domain-model-and-state-machine.yolopilot.md:668:    ./prompts/09-initial-system-diagram-and-adr.yolopilot.jsonlines:12:{\\\"color\\\": \\\"cyan\\\", \\\"emoji\\\": \\\"\\\\ud83d\\\\udee0\\\\ufe0f\\\", \\\"event_type\\\": \\\"Command Finished\\\", \\\"message\\\": \\\"completed, exit 0: /bin/zsh -lc 'rg --files'\\\", \\\"raw_event\\\": {\\\"item\\\": {\\\"aggregated_output\\\": \\\"secrets.example.yaml\\\\nprompts/00-project-charter.codex.jsonlines\\\\nprompts/36-conversation-memory-summaries.md\\\\nprompts/99-release-checklist-and-future-roadmap.md\\\\nprompts/44-pitch-generation-pipeline.md\\\\nprompts/08-repo-quality-tooling.yolopilot.jsonlines\\\\nprompts/04-docker-compose-foundation.codex.jsonlines\\\\nprompts/05-backend-settings-and-secrets-loading.summary.md\\\\nprompts/08-repo-quality-tooling.codex.jsonlines\\\\nprompts/42-story-setup-brief-form.md\\\\nprompts/07-developer-bootstrap-scripts.md\\\\nprompts/06-gitignore-and-secrets-hygiene.yolopilot.md\\\\nprompts/20-frontend-app-shell-and-routing.md\\\\nprompts/52-bedtime-safety-and-content-guidelines.md\\\\nprompts/02-vite-react-scaffold.md\\\\nprompts/78-download-endpoints-and-object-access.md\\\\nprompts/01-monorepo-skeleton.md\\\\nprompts/13-storage-abstraction-and-buckets.md\\\\nprompts/48-save-the-cat-beat-sheet-generation.md\\\\nprompts/95-ci-pipeline.md\\\\nprompts/46-ch