{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The current backend has the relational models but no reference-data loader or catalog query abstraction. I\u2019m mapping the smallest change set that gives later prompts a clean source of truth: human-editable seed data, an idempotent loader...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_28", "text": "The current backend has the relational models but no reference-data loader or catalog query abstraction. I\u2019m mapping the smallest change set that gives later prompts a clean source of truth: human-editable seed data, an idempotent loader, and read helpers/tests that prove the DB can drive the selectors.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 57, "prompt_index": 13, "prompt_name": "12 \u2014 Seed the Genre and Tone Catalog", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T22:56:32-07:00"}
