{"color": "cyan", "emoji": "\ud83d\udee0\ufe0f", "event_type": "Command Finished", "message": "completed, exit 0: /bin/zsh -lc \"sed -n '1,220p' backend/tests/conftest.py\"", "raw_event": {"item": {"aggregated_output": "import os\nimport sys\nfrom collections.abc import Iterator\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nimport pytest\nfrom fastapi.testclient import TestClient\n\nBACKEND_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nTEST_ENVIRONMENT_DEFAULTS = {\n    \"STORYTELLER_SECRETS_FILE\": \"\",\n    \"STORYTELLER_DATABASE_URL\": (\"postgresql://storyteller:storyteller@postgres:5432/storyteller\"),\n    \"STORYTELLER_GEMINI_API_KEY\": \"test-gemini-key\",\n    \"STORYTELLER_GCS_ENDPOINT\": \"http://gcs:4443\",\n    \"STORYTELLER_GCS_PROJECT_ID\": \"storyteller-local\",\n    \"STORYTELLER_GCS_PUBLIC_URL\": \"http://localhost:8568\",\n    \"STORYTELLER_GCS_SESSIONS_BUCKET_NAME\": \"storyteller-sessions\",\n    \"STORYTELLER_GCS_AUDIO_BUCKET_NAME\": \"storyteller-audio\",\n    \"STORYTELLER_GCS_EXPORTS_BUCKET_NAME\": \"storyteller-exports\",\n}\n\nif str(BACKEND_ROOT) not in sys.path:\n    sys.path.insert(0, str(BACKEND_ROOT))\n\nfor name, value in TEST_ENVIRONMENT_DEFAULTS.items():\n    os.environ.setdefault(name, value)\n\n\n@pytest.fixture\ndef client() -> Iterator[TestClient]:\n    from app.main import create_app\n    from app.settings import get_settings\n\n    get_settings.cache_clear()\n\n    with TestClient(create_app()) as test_client:\n        yield test_client\n\n    get_settings.cache_clear()\n", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc \"sed -n '1,220p' backend/tests/conftest.py\"", "exit_code": 0, "id": "item_33", "status": "completed", "type": "command_execution"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 66, "prompt_index": 13, "prompt_name": "12 \u2014 Seed the Genre and Tone Catalog", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T22:56:32-07:00"}
{"color": "cyan", "emoji": "\ud83d\udee0\ufe0f", "event_type": "Command Finished", "message": "completed, exit 0: /bin/zsh -lc \"sed -n '1,220p' docs/README.md\"", "raw_event": {"item": {"aggregated_output": "# Docs\n\nThis directory holds product notes, architecture notes, ADRs, diagrams, and other reviewer-oriented documentation.\n\nCurrent entrypoints:\n\n- `product-brief.md`: product expectations and workflow\n- `architecture-overview.md`: target system shape and durable boundaries\n- `domain-model.md`: durable session entities, workflow-stage contract, and stage-state rules\n- `system-diagram.md`: one-page runtime diagram for browser, API, worker, storage, and Gemini flows\n- `contributing.md`: shared quality commands and code-style conventions\n- `adr/`: architecture decision records, starting with the core runtime architecture ADR\n", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc \"sed -n '1,220p' docs/README.md\"", "exit_code": 0, "id": "item_32", "status": "completed", "type": "command_execution"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 67, "prompt_index": 13, "prompt_name": "12 \u2014 Seed the Genre and Tone Catalog", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T22:56:32-07:00"}
{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I\u2019ve got enough context to lock the implementation shape. Plan is: 1. Add a human-editable backend-owned catalog file plus a small loader/normalizer layer. 2. Add an idempotent seed command that upserts `genres` and `tone_profiles` from...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_34", "text": "I\u2019ve got enough context to lock the implementation shape. Plan is:\n1. Add a human-editable backend-owned catalog file plus a small loader/normalizer layer.\n2. Add an idempotent seed command that upserts `genres` and `tone_profiles` from that catalog.\n3. Add read-side catalog helpers so later API prompts can fetch genres and genre-filtered tones without frontend hard-coding.\n4. Cover the behavior with backend tests, then update docs and the backend command references.\n5. Verify with targeted tests, repo quality checks, and a real seed run against a disposable database before writing the task summary and commit(s).", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 68, "prompt_index": 13, "prompt_name": "12 \u2014 Seed the Genre and Tone Catalog", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T22:56:43-07:00"}
