{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I found one gap the schema does not cover yet: `tone_profiles` can store descriptors and bedtime notes, but not the per-tone planning hints that prompt 12 explicitly calls for. I\u2019m adding that field as a small follow-on migration instead...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_40", "text": "I found one gap the schema does not cover yet: `tone_profiles` can store descriptors and bedtime notes, but not the per-tone planning hints that prompt 12 explicitly calls for. I\u2019m adding that field as a small follow-on migration instead of trying to smuggle planning hints into an unrelated JSON column.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 78, "prompt_index": 13, "prompt_name": "12 \u2014 Seed the Genre and Tone Catalog", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T22:57:13-07:00"}
