{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented the prompt-12 catalog seed work. The backend now has a human-editable YAML catalog, typed catalog models and query helpers, an idempotent seed CLI, a follow-on migration for `tone_profiles.default_planning_hints`, new tests,...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_79", "text": "Implemented the prompt-12 catalog seed work. The backend now has a human-editable YAML catalog, typed catalog models and query helpers, an idempotent seed CLI, a follow-on migration for `tone_profiles.default_planning_hints`, new tests, and docs tying the catalog back to the prompt pack. The checkpoint commit is `ba8cfc8` with message `feat(prompt-12): seed genres and tones`.\n\nThe required reviewer summary was written to [prompts/12-seed-genres-and-tones.summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/prompts/12-seed-genres-and-tones.summary.md). Key implementation entrypoints are [backend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml), [backend/app/services/catalog.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/services/catalog.py), and [backend/app/seed_catalog.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/seed_catalog.py).\n\nVerification completed:\n- `make backend-format`\n- `make backend-format-check`\n- `make backend-lint`\n- `make backend-test`\n- `make check`\n- End-to-end seed verification against a disposable migrated SQLite DB with `python -m alembic upgrade head`, `python -m app.seed_catalog`, and `python -m app.seed_catalog --dry-run`\n\nNo browser or screenshot QA was needed because this prompt only changed backend/data/docs. The main unsupervised assumption was that the repo did not actually contain a standalone upstream genre/tone research artifact, so I derived the initial catalog from the visible prompt-pack guidance and documented that explicitly in the summary and catalog docs.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 143, "prompt_index": 13, "prompt_name": "12 \u2014 Seed the Genre and Tone Catalog", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T23:06:10-07:00"}
